The presidential candidate of the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) in last Saturday’s election, Atiku Abubakar has assured President Muhammadu Buhari and all Nigerians that he would reclaim his “stolen mandate” in court. Atiku, a former Vice President who addressed a world press conference on Wednesday in Abuja, said the outcome of the election which saw Buhari of the All Progressives Congress (APC) as winner did not reflect the will of the people. Detail later……. Atiku: APC has failed Nigeria Buhari failed to deliver his mandate – Atiku Kebbi: Gov. Bagudu delivers polling unit to Buhari, APC